dct_title_s: Topographic maps of Afghanistan and Kabul
dct_description_sm: Computer disks include shapes files of Afghanistan and Kabul.

CD 1. 34 provinces shapefiles; specific city data including airports, bridges, government buildings, graveyards, streams, district boundaries, roads, squares, etc.; land cover; physical; provincial; rivers; roads; settlements as of November 2004; soil.  CD 2. Kabul data including bridges, education facilities, contour lines, government buildings, land use, road network, building footprint, trees, landmarks, hotels, restaurants, etc.
System requirements: IBM-compatible PC; CD-ROM drive.
dct_rights_sm: These data are licensed by Stanford Libraries and are available to Stanford University affiliates only. Affiliates are limited to current faculty, staff and students. Non affiliates seeking access should contact the publisher directly. These data may not be reproduced or used for any purpose without permission.
